#: inc/AdInitiator.php:54
msgid "Switching between pages or categories can usually take some time. With this plugin you can enjoy a fast loading of your tables."
msgstr "在页面或分类之间切换通常需要一些时间。有了这个插件，您就可以享受表格的快速加载。"

#: inc/AdInitiator.php:54
msgid "Switch pages without page reload"
msgstr "无需重新加载页面即可切换页面"

#: inc/AdInitiator.php:54
msgid "Shop managers with many products also have to maintain numerous categories. Wouldn't it be helpful to maintain the product categories and attributes more elegantly?"
msgstr "拥有众多产品的店长还必须维护众多分类。如果能更巧妙地维护产品分类和属性，岂不是更好？"

#: inc/AdInitiator.php:54
msgid "Supports WooCommerce products"
msgstr "支持 WooCommerce 产品"

#: inc/AdInitiator.php:54
msgid "In the PRO version you can also enable the tree on pages and custom post types."
msgstr "在专业版中，您还可以在页面和自定义文章类型中启用树形结构。"

#: inc/AdInitiator.php:54
msgid "Do you maintain many categories? The default view of the categories can be a bit confusing, can't it? This plugin creates an explorer-like tree on the left side of your posts table. Create, rename, delete or rearrange your categories with a single click!"
msgstr "您有很多分类吗？默认的分类视图可能会有点混乱，不是吗？这个插件可以在文章表的左侧创建一个类似于资源管理器的树状结构。只需单击一下，即可创建、重命名、删除或重新排列分类！"

#: inc/AdInitiator.php:54
msgid "Full control over your categories"
msgstr "完全控制您的分类"

